金的内容，不知道该怎么办了，请大家帮帮忙，出个主意，谢谢(*≧∪≦) ！！ 介绍一下公司情况，两家都是双休，薪资大概率两家差的不多。拿到offer的是民营企业，且是正式工，工作内容方面比较单一，学到的东西有限；等结果的是外企（不提倡加班），但是是外包（和第三方签订劳动合同，但明确表明和正式工待遇一样），工作内容丰富，能学到比较多的东西。 本人情况：属于实验技术岗，刚工作两年裸辞换一个城市找工作，想提升自己，提高一下竞争力，但也想要挣钱。希望能得到各位的帮助，非常感谢 ！！！"},"attached_info":"CkAI0aTWvrL/qvgUEAMaCTExMTIzOTQ5NyDtwcq4BjAAOExAG3IKMTMxMzA0OTI1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"36 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-8f887cd7fd269e4a2c0c31fe202ebacb_1440w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1729600046.286588","card_id":"Q_351040018","target":{"id":351040018,"title":"已知在某种进制下2×3=10，那么在该进制下3×5等于多少？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/351040018","type":"question","created":1571228663,"answer_count":91,"follower_count":111,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1291,12223,31637],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I0aTWvrL/qvgUEAMaCDQwMjg3MDE3IPeXnO0FMAA4b0AccgkzNTEwNDAwMTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"36 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ecc43f6b4012c86ca081607d7e04a81d_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1729600046.287130","card_id":"Q_671400718","target":{"id":671400718,"title":"回避型依恋真正的需要是什么？如何关照他们的情绪并跟他们相处？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/671400718","type":"question","created":1727422224,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":86,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[404,5993,405458,1402314,3723016],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I0aTWvrL/qvgUEAMaCTExMDc5NzUzNiCQvtm3BjAAOFZAHXIJNjcxNDAwNzE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail